hadiths[6]{hadithnumber,text}:
942,mein Najad ki taraf Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang (zaatur-Riqaa') mein Sharik tha. dushman se muqable ke waqt ham ne safain baandhiin. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khof ki Namaz padhai (to ham mein se) aik jamat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhney mein Sharik ho gaee aur doosra giroh dushman ke muqable mein khada raha. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhney walon ke sath aik rukoo aur 2 sajdey kiye. phir ye log lot kar us jamat ki jagah aagey jisne abhi Namaz nahi padhi thi. ab dusri jamat aai. unke sath bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik rukoo aur 2 sajdey kiye. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam pher diya. us giroh mein se har shakhs khada hua aur us ne akeley akeley aik rukoo aur 2 sajdey ada kiye.
943,jab jang mein log aik doosrey se guth jayen to khadey khadey Namaz padh lein aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni riwayat mein izafa aur kya hai ke agar kaafir bahut sarey hon ke musalmanon ko dam na leney dein to khadey-khadey aur sawar reh kar (jis taur mumkin ho) isharon se hi sahii magar Namaz padh lein.
944,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur doosrey log bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein khadey huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer kahi to logon ne bhi takbeer kahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo kya to logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rukoo aur sajda kar liya tha wo khadey-khadey apne bhaiyon ki nigrani kartey rahe aur doosra giroh aaya. (jo ab tak hifazat ke liye dushman ke muqaabla mein khada raha baad mein) usne bhi rukoo aur sajdey kiye. sab log Namaz mein they lekin log aik doosrey ki hifazat kar rahe they.
945,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) Khandaq ki jang ke din kuffaar ko bura bhala kehtey huey aaey aur arz karne lagey ke ya Rasulullah! suraj doobney hi ko hai aur maine to ab tak Asr ki Namaz nahi padhi, is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke b-khudaa maine bhi abhi tak nahi padhi unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir aap '' Bathan'' ki taraf gaey (jo Madina mein aik maidan tha) aur wuzu karke aap ne wahan suraj ghurub honey ke baad Asr ki Namaz padhi, phir iske baad namaze-Maghrib padhi."
946,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Khandaq ki jang se farigh huey ( Abu-Sufiyan lautey ( to ham se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi shakhs banu-Quraiza ke mohalle mein pahunchne se pahley namaze-Asr na padhey lekin jab Asr ka waqt aaya to kuchh sahaba ne raaste hi mein Namaz padh li aur kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ham banu-Quraiza ke mohalle mein pahunchne par namaze-Asr padhengey aur kuchh hazraat ka khayal ye hua ke hamein Namaz padh leni chahiye kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka maqsad ye nahi tha ke Namaz qaza kar lein. phir jab aap se iska zikr kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi par bhi malaamat nahi farmai.
947,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki Namaz andherey hi mein padha di, phir sawar huey ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar pahunch gaey aur wahan ke yahudiyon ko aap ke aaney ki itlaa ho gai) aur farmaya ( Allahu-akbar ( khaibar par barbadi aa gaee. ham to jab kisi qaum ke aangan mein utar jayen to daraaiye huey logon ki subah manhoos hogi. us waqt khaibar ke Yahudi galiyon mein ye kehtey huey bhag rahe they ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lashkar samet aa gaey. rawi ne kaha ke (riwaayat mein) lafz (hamees) lashkar ke mana mein hai. aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fateh hui. ladney waley jawan qatl kar diye gaey, auratein aur bachchey qaid huey. ittifaq se Safiya, Dahiya Kalbi ke hisse mein aaein. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko miliin aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah kya aur aazadi unka mehar qarar paya. Abdul-Azeez ne Sabit se puchha : abu-Muhammad! kya tum ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se malum kya tha ke Safiya ka mehar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muqarrar kya tha unhon-ne jawab diya ke khud unhein ko unke mehar mein de diya tha. kaha ke abu-Muhammad is par muskuraa diye."
